reviewText: Im satisfied because I got what I wanted and its the whole first season so yeah.
I've been waiting for the whole seasons to come out on DVD!! However, when I received it the case was damaged! Cracked edges on both front and back sides! Not too happy :(

It showed up a day early awesome but some episodes are out of order all episodes are there have to be patient watch 1 episode at a time write down episode list if you want to watch them in order it's a great show I recommend for anyone to buy young and old
